folder: Parsons Boulevard & Sanford Avenue, Queens, NY
text:
Parsons Boulevard, at the N.E. corner of Sanford Avenue, showing the Malcolm Graham Mansion of 1873, a frame structure.
It was known in 1891 as the Club House.
P. L. Sperr  April 13, 1927

folder: Sanford Avenue & Parsons Boulevard, Queens, NY

Sanford Avenue,north side, between Parsons Boulevard and 147th

NO REPRODUCTIONS  April 13, 192
